  volumenAudio: 0.8
  textoFragmento: "Child.\r\nCome on, come on! I have to get out of here...\r\nAhhh!\u2026
    cobwebs\u2026 they\u2019re everywhere\u2026\n\r\nwitch\r\nSpiders\u2026! There
    are spiders everywhere!\r\nKeep them away from me! Spiders, noooo!.\n\r\nChild.\r\nThe
    witch... she\u2019s afraid of them?\r\nWell\u2026 that\u2019s something I didn\u2019t
    expect...\r\nMaybe... that could come in handy later.\r\nAll right... time to
    get out before she comes back!\r"
